---
---
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-24 relative overflow-visible">
  <!-- Glowing anti-cut decoration -->
  <div class="absolute -top-12 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full max-w-2xl h-32 bg-primary/10 rounded-full blur-[80px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="bg-blue-950 rounded-[3.5rem] p-12 md:p-24 text-center text-white relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl reveal group">
    <!-- Background Decoration -->
    <div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 w-96 h-96 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none group-hover:bg-white/15 transition-colors duration-700"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none group-hover:bg-primary/30 transition-colors duration-700"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 space-y-10">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight text-white mb-0 tracking-tighter">
          Não espere mais para<br>cuidar da sua <span class="text-primary italic font-medium">comunicação</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-blue-50/70 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed italic">
          Agende uma avaliação completa e descubra como a fonoaudiologia pode transformar sua qualidade de vida.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center pt-4">
        <a href="#agendamento" class="bg-white text-blue-950 px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 active:scale-95">
          Quero agendar agora
        </a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/seu-numero" class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md text-white border border-white/20 px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl font-bold text-xl hover:bg-white/20 transition-all hover:scale-[1.02]">
          Dúvidas? Chamar no Zap
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="pt-8 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 opacity-30 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
        </svg>
        Ambiente Seguro e Profissional
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
